    <p>I am very happy and grate­ful to re­ceive the Sin­ga­poRe dis­cov­ers vouch­ers, and will think of a num­ber of ways to use them.</p>
    <p>As se­niors are of­ten hand­i­capped by health is­sues and in­fir­mity, they need their helpers to as­sist them.</p>
    <p>If the vouch­ers can be used for the helpers ac­com­pa­ny­ing the se­niors, they would be even more mean­ing­ful and use­ful.</p>
    <p>I hope the au­thor­i­ties can look into this so that our helpers can come along and look af­ter us.</p>


